hr.fer.zemris.java.custom.scripting.exec

Class ObjectMultistack

  • java.lang.Object
    • hr.fer.zemris.java.custom.scripting.exec.ObjectMultistack

  • public class ObjectMultistack
extends Object
    This class represents a collection where multiples values can be assigned to a single key. These multiple values are stored on a LIFO basis and are retrieved as such. It comes equipped with methods for adding and retrieving values according to their keys.
    Author:
    Filip Džidić
